codeText: public EventGenerator<K, E> newSessionGeneratorForKey(K key, long globalWatermark) {_		EventGenerator<K, E> eventGenerator = latestGeneratorsByKey.get(key)___		if (eventGenerator == null) {_			SessionConfiguration<K, E> sessionConfiguration = SessionConfiguration.of(_					key,_					0,_					maxSessionEventGap,_					globalWatermark,_					timelyEventsPerSession,_					eventFactory)__			SessionGeneratorConfiguration<K, E> sessionGeneratorConfiguration =_					new SessionGeneratorConfiguration<>(sessionConfiguration, generatorConfiguration)__			eventGenerator = new SessionEventGeneratorImpl<>(sessionGeneratorConfiguration, randomGenerator)__		} else {_			eventGenerator = eventGenerator.getNextGenerator(globalWatermark)__		}_		latestGeneratorsByKey.put(key, eventGenerator)__		++producedGeneratorsCount__		return eventGenerator__	}
